entries.arrived_at_delivery: You are at the correct location pilot, the freighter should be there any second.
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.autorewardbody: You did a good job delivering those kashyyyk bantha pelts.  Payment enclosed.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: I got it. Tell Kerssoc the pelts have been secured.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Lets do this quickly, I don't like the look of all those laser burns on your ship.
entries.failed_destroyed: Return to Kerssoc immediately pilot. We may have to start over.
entries.found_loc_d: Deliver the pelts to our freighter at these coordinates.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, I'm ready to transfer those pelts to my ship.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Make sure that you have eliminated nearby threats before starting the docking sequence as both you and the freighter will be very vulnerable while transferring the pelts.
entries.quest_location_d: A freighter will meet with you in the Corellia system. They will take the Kashyyyk bantha pelts and distribute them.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: You have been provided with these coordinates for the delivery. Try to avoid any bandits or poachers in the area.
entries.split_quest_alert: Kerssoc has another task for you. Head to the Kashyyyk system and escort some inbound supplies.
entries.title: Corellia system: Deliver the Kashyyyk bantha pelts.
entries.title_d: Deliver Kashyyyk bantha pelts to a freighter in the Corellia System.
